Write a Java program to reverse a linked list.
answer: public ListNode reverseList(ListNode head) { ListNode prev = null; ListNode curr = head; while (curr != null) { ListNode nextTemp = curr.next; curr.next = prev; prev = curr; curr = nextTemp; } return prev; }

Write a function to rotate an array of integers by k positions to the right.
answer:
def rotate_array(arr, k):
    n = len(arr)
    k = k % n
    arr[:] = arr[-k:] + arr[:-k]

Write an algorithm to find the first and last occurrence of a target element in a sorted array.
answer:
def find_first_last_occurrence(nums, target):
    left = bisect.bisect_left(nums, target)
    right = bisect.bisect_right(nums, target)
    return [left, right - 1] if left < len(nums) and nums[left] == target else [-1, -1]
